{"type":"message","id":"214a0765","parentId":"2273b5e1","timestamp":"2026-03-02T20:23:59.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md content from the project context. It's already loaded in the workspace files:\n\n## /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n# HEARTBEAT.md - 自动备份任务\n\n## 任务：检查并提交未保存的修改\n\n每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 目录是否有未提交的修改，如有则按功能划分 commit 并 push 到远端。\n\n### 检查步骤\n\n1. **进入工作目录**\n   ```bashclaw\n   ```\n\n   cd ~/.open\n2. **检查 git 状态**\n   ```bash\n   git status\n   ```\n\n3. **如果有未提交的修改，按以下规则分组**：\n\n   | 修改类型 | Commit 消息前缀 |\n   |----------|-----------------|\n   | 新技能/技能更新 | `skill:` |\n   | 配置文件修改 | `config:` |\n   | 工作区文件 | `workspace:` |\n   | 文档更新 | `docs:` |\n   | 其他修改 | `chore:` |\n\n4. **执行提交和推送**\n   ```bash\n   git add -A\n   git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"\n   git push\n   ```\n\n5. **记录日志**（可选）\n   - 将本次提交信息记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n### 执行频率\n- 建议：每天 1 次（如上午 9:00 或下午 15:00）\n- 手动触发也可\n\n### 注意事项\n- 如果是敏感信息（如 credentials），不要 commit\n- 优先确保重要修改已同步\n  \n现在需要检查是否有未保存的更改。当前时间是凌晨 4:23，接近建议的备份时间，但执行频率是每天一次，所以我应该先查看当前的 git 状态。","thinkingSignature":"e96ba042105fc8e4fa8deb6b9297bdee4d6fe447e917bb448136f930ab65982e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n1tsxrcn7q1q_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw && git status","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":407,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":18384,"totalTokens":18827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772483031770}}
